              font-size: 14px;
              color: #666666;
              line-height: 1.7;
              margin-bottom: 20px;
            ">Custom-fabricated aluminum channel letter signs with front-lit, halo-lit or combination LED illumination. The gold standard for retail storefront branding.</p>
            
            <a href="{{ pages['sign-category'].url }}?category=storefront" style="
              display: inline-flex;
              align-items: center;
              gap: 8px;
              color: #0066CC;
              font-weight: 700;
              font-size: 14px;
              text-decoration: none;
              transition: all 0.3s;
            " onmouseover="this.style.gap='12px'" onmouseout="this.style.gap='8px'">
              Explore Storefront Signs
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Card 2: Reception & Studio Signs -->
        <div style="
          background: white;
          border-radius: 16px;
          overflow: hidden;
          box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
