              line-height: 1.7;
              margin-bottom: 20px;
            ">Soft, premium halo glow that elevates any brand. Push through signs with acrylic faces and stainless steel returns for a refined, modern look.</p>
            
            <a href="{{ pages['sign-category'].url }}?category=reception" style="
              display: inline-flex;
