              font-weight: 700;
              color: #1a1a1a;
              margin-bottom: 12px;
            ">Coffee Shops & Restaurants</h3>
            
            <p style="
              font-size: 14px;
              color: #666666;
              line-height: 1.7;
              margin-bottom: 20px;
            ">Lightbox signs, cabinet signs and face-lit fixtures designed for high-traffic main street visibility. UL listed components throughout.</p>
            
            <a href="{{ pages['sign-category'].url }}?category=restaurant" style="
